                <div class="req-icon">🚚</div>
                <div class="req-body">
                    <h3 class="text-base bold mb-02">Pickup address (only if originals are needed)</h3>
                    <ul class="flex-col gap-05 text-s opacity-90">
                        <li>For sticker apostille or SDM/Notary requirements, we arrange secure door-to-door courier.</li>
